    "The survey was implemented in Google Forms.",
    "It commenced by asking participants to provide informed consent in line with Cardiff University's guidelines.",
    "Participants were then asked to watch a 1-min overview over ChatGTP on YouTube (https://www.",
    "youtube.com/watch?v=aIO9it4HFiQ) to make sure that they are familiar with the basic principles of LLMs.",
    "Further videos and a blog post were presented as optional additional material."
